		"txt":"[{\"createTime\":1482268183000,\"description\":\"[]\",\"descriptionJson\":[],\"id\":575,\"instruction\":\"The Load Balancer can automatically detect the availability status of back-end machine through the policy of performance check. Once finding any exception of the machine, it will stop forwarding traffic to this machine and restore automatically after the machine operates normally. The users can also manually add or delete back-end service machines based on practical business demands. Resources can be deployed in different AZs if higher availability is needed. \",\"lang\":\"en\",\"langId\":6,\"name\":\"Flexible Adjustment to Business Load Scale; High-availability Demand\",\"operator\":\"zhuohao\",\"picUrl\":\"http://www-jcloud-com.oss.cn-stag-1.jcloudcs.com/en/f60c5977-81d6-4f62-ab8b-64b161a4e70b20171206181033.png\",\"productId\":396,\"sort\":0,\"status\":0},{\"createTime\":1482268183000,\"description\":\"[]\",\"descriptionJson\":[],\"id\":576,\"instruction\":\"Load Balancer (LB) can be configured in an Intranet environment, and provide external services by Associate EIP. Therefore, the Intranet structure can be concealed, so as to enhance the system security. Besides, a more secure protection system can be built by setting a firewall or taking other measures.\",\"lang\":\"en\",\"langId\":7,\"name\":\"High Security Demand\",\"operator\":\"zhuohao\",\"picUrl\":\"http://www-jcloud-com.oss.cn-stag-1.jcloudcs.com/en/9748a8c2-c301-4e18-8018-0c18a6b660d120170426103758.jpg\",\"productId\":396,\"sort\":0,\"status\":0},{\"description\":\"[]\",\"descriptionJson\":[],\"id\":607,\"instruction\":\"Support unvarnished transmission of the real IP address of the client through Load Balancer under HTTP monitoring protocol, making it convenient to analyze the source of customer and make statistics on the operation and maintenance data\",\"lang\":\"en\",\"langId\":74,\"name\":\"Real Customer Source Analysis\",\"picUrl\":\"http://www-jcloud-com.oss.cn-stag-1.jcloudcs.com/en/f49b0dd2-d601-40ad-85ae-31fb21aaa4ca20170426110104.jpg\",\"productId\":396,\"sort\":0,\"status\":0},{\"description\":\"[]\",\"descriptionJson\":[],\"id\":608,\"instruction\":\"Load Balancer can be used to evenly distribute the traffic to multiple Virtual Machines at the rear end, and set up different traffic distribution schemes through the dispatch algorithm, giving a solution to the system impact caused by mass-flow and burst traffic. It can be applied in conventional websites, large-scale business websites, sec-killing, panic buying or other business systems that may lead to the increase of burst traffic.\",\"lang\":\"en\",\"langId\":75,\"name\":\"Cope with mass traffic and burst traffic\",\"picUrl\":\"http://www-jcloud-com.oss.cn-stag-1.jcloudcs.com/en/37ea8dea-ce53-4510-877e-9ea42fbf884320170426110205.jpg\",\"productId\":396,\"sort\":0,\"status\":0}]",
